data.description: Don't miss this custom-built home on a beautiful 5-acre estate! This home has everything you have been looking for! Near Silverwood amusement park and Farragut State Park. Custom-built two-story home with two master suites, with expansive 30x40 insulated shop, (2) 12x14 doors, set against a wooded backdrop, landscaped yard, wooded privacy surrounding the lot, storage shed, and much more! Enjoy the elk, deer, moose, turkeys, and other wildlife from your rocking chair on your covered back porch, entertain in the large open living room with vaulted ceilings and a new two-story fireplace. Views over the landscaped and wooded acreage, or just relax on the back patio, or in the pool and enjoy the privacy in your own Idaho getaway. This home offers everything someone would want from an Idaho getaway. Maintained paved roads and situated close to shopping, highway access, and convenient to Coeur d'Alene, Spokane, and Sandpoint. A home worth taking the time to see.
